    <item>
      <title>英国交易员认为，英镑下跌抵消了债券市场 2023 年以来的最佳表现</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-17/pound-falls-as-weak-retail-data-deals-fresh-blow-to-confidence</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国借贷成本即将创下一年多以来的最大三日跌幅，但由于对政府财政状况的担忧挥之不去，交易员们认为英镑的走势不会有任何缓解。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-17/pound-falls-as-weak-retail-data-deals-fresh-blow-to-confidence</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 17 Jan 2025 07:45:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
